text: Kylie Cosmetics, LLC is an American cosmetics company founded by Kylie Jenner. The company began selling Kylie Lip Kits on November 30, 2015. In 2018, Forbes reported that the company was valued at $800 million and in March 2019 valued the company at $900 million. ==References== Category:2014 establishments in California Category:Cosmetics companies Category:Companies based in California Category:Oxnard, California
